title: The Fugitive S02E27 Runner in the Dark DivX
description:
The Fugitive
S02E27
Runner in the Dark

Airdate: March 30, 1965

    * One of 15 episodes from Season Two which have not been released on DVD
    * Remastered audio and video from VHS TV rip
    * Original music, not a synthesized replacement track!


Surrounded by police, Kimble (David Janssen) seeks sanctuary in a home for the blind.

Brady: Ed Begley. Stern: Peter Haskell. Claire: Diana van der Vlis.
